    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Articles of dining-room furniture intended to dispense with the services of a waiter at table. It comprises an upright pole bearing one or more trays or shelves, sometimes revolving. On these are placed glasses, dishes, and other table requisites.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
